# dotctl waybar decorator — round (Powerline half circles)
# Substitutes the canonical pointed chevrons with their round equivalents.
#
# Format: each non-comment line is  FROM TO  (whitespace-separated). At apply
# time dotctl reads the file for the active WAYBAR_DECOR and substitutes
# FROM → TO in the waybar config.jsonc.

# U+E0B0 right chevron →  U+E0B4 right half-circle
 

# U+E0B2 left chevron  →  U+E0B6 left half-circle
 
